# Hootner Project Rules

## TypeScript
- Use strict mode with verbatimModuleSyntax
- Prefer type over interface for simple types
- Use const assertions for literal types
- Import types with `import type`

## Monorepo
- Shared packages must export compiled .js from dist/
- Use workspace protocol for internal dependencies
- Run affected tests only via `turbo run test --affected`

## Code Style
- Single quotes for strings
- 2-space indentation
- Trailing commas in multiline
- No semicolons (Prettier handles)

## Testing
- Use Vitest for all tests
- Follow AAA pattern
- Mock external APIs
- Aim for 80%+ coverage
